  section
    h2 React
    p.
      React uses its own abstraction of the HTML DOM. You delegate performance
      to React (which is a good thing) when performing DOM operations.
    p You would return
    pre
      code.hljs.html.
        React.render(&lt;h1>Hello World&lt;/h1>, document.body);

